reviewText: Truly the number one martial artist he pushed the boundaries his speed and strength won't be matched
Not detailed enough but ok for it's time period.
Never seen a documentary of Bruce Lee like this before

Alot of this film footage was filmed right after Bruce Lee passed away. The music is kind of depressing though. But it is a great documentary, I have been looking for it for years in the states. It's ironic that I found this movie from a distributor in Italy that had the movie! It's a region B movie so I have to play it from my PC, but I am happy that i finally found it. If you are a Bruce Lee fan you need to have this in your collection.
